These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different games are played: backgammon, poker, go, whist, domino, billiard
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, cycling, parkour, basketball, sailing
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing poker##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Game   | billiard | backgammon  | go    | whist  | poker      | domino    |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | sailing | basketball | water-polo | parkour | cycling |

