.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: emerald, grey, purple, aquamarine, lavender, yellow
There 6 different types of food: carrot, radish, onion, pumpkin, grapes, lettuce
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
6. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating onion##1
7. the person who likes yellow is the person eating lettuce##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
9. the person who likes emerald is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Color   | emerald   | lavender | grey | yellow | aquamarine     | purple  |
| Food           | onion | radish    | carrot      | lettuce  | pumpkin | grapes |

