.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, pomegranate, pumpkin, cabbage, broccoli, lettuce
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, tea, almond-milk, milk, juice, iced-tea
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cabbage##1
9. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Food   | cabbage   | lettuce   | broccoli      | pomegranate | cauliflower  | pumpkin   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | water | tea   | juice | milk |

