.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
House: colonial, palace, tower, art-deco, cape-cod, wooden
There are 6 different favourite colors: chestnut, white, fuchsia, light-blue, brown, yellow
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
2. the tower house is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who likes yellow is the art-deco house##1
6. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| House   | tower  | art-deco | colonial      | palace  | wooden | cape-cod |
| Color     | chestnut | yellow  | brown | fuchsia | light-blue  | white    |

