.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, train, van, subway, trike, bus
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, ice-hockey, snowboarding, baseball, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Transport         | subway | bus | motorbike | trike | train | van  |
| Sport   | skiing  | snowboarding  | ice-hockey  | rowing | baseball      | tennis |

