.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: orange, brown, aquamarine, emerald, yellow, azure
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, paramedic, musician, designer, scientist, pilot
1. the pilot is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the designer is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the designer is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
5. the scientist is the person who likes azure##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the musician##1
7. the lawyer is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
9. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Color   | azure    | aquamarine    | orange | yellow     | brown   | emerald     |
| Job   | scientist | paramedic | pilot | musician | designer | lawyer |

