4. the person watching western movies is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating banana##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
9. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
