.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, entrepreneur, teacher, pilot, engineer
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, march, february, december, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the dancer is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the fisherman##1
4. the teacher is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
6. the fisherman is on the far left##1
7. the engineer is the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Job          | fisherman | engineer   | pilot  | entrepreneur    | teacher  | dancer |
| Birthday   | march   | may | november | january | february | december |

