.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, guinea-pig, cat, hedgehog, pony
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, davidoff, game, pall-mall, ritmeester, tiparillo
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
4. the game-smoker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the ferret is the pall-mall-smoker##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Pet   | pony    | ferret     | guinea-pig | fish | cat | hedgehog   |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | pall-mall | ritmeester | game   | montecristo    | davidoff |

