.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
There 6 different types of food: pear, eggplant, kale, lemon, grapefruit, lime
House: tower, futuristic, palace, modern, colonial, victorian
1. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the modern house is the person eating lemon##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the palace house##1
6. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
7. the person eating kale is on the left of the tower house##1
8. the futuristic house is on the left of the person eating lime##1
9. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Food   | grapefruit | lime | lemon    | eggplant | kale  | pear |
| House     | futuristic    | colonial | modern | victorian   | palace | tower    |

