.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, may, july, august, june, february
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, yellow, ivory, lavender, orange, black
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
8. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
9. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Birthday         | july | may | june | august | october    | february |
| Color   | red   | orange      | lavender        | ivory    | yellow | black  |

