1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsaconite is the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of disco##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
9. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Flower     | daffodil  | aconite       | iris   | balloon-flower      | lily | begonia          |
| Music-Genre   | disco | electronic | metal | techno | dubstep | classical |

