1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
9. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure     | spy       | comedy  | musical | satire    |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | turtle | horse | mouse | goat  | frog |

 